LORIA/SYNALP EmotionML API v0.2

Packages
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml The main package of LORIA/SYNALP EmotionML.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.descriptors Contains all the aspects that describe an Emotion including Category, Dimension, Appraisal and ActionTendency.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.examples Contains examples on how to import/export and customize emotions.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.examples.custom.emotion Contains examples on how to import a custom emotion.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.examples.custom.info.dom Contains examples on how to import/export info elements using DOM.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.examples.custom.info.jaxb Contains examples on how to import/export info elements using JAXB.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.exceptions Contains EmotionML exceptions.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.info Contains Info element and InfoCarrier.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors Contains all processors, exporters/importers and validators for EmotionML.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors.jaxb Contains the importer and exporter for the Info elements using JAXB.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.processors.json Contains the importer and exporter for the JSON format.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.tests Contains some tests.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.vocabularies Contains elements related to Vocabularies.
fr.loria.synalp.emotionml.vocabularies.predefined Contains all predefined vocabularies that can be found on http://www.w3.org/TR/emotion-voc/xml.
